---
// Callback / Contact section
---

<section class="section-image callback-bg" id="callback">
    <div class="callback-overlay"></div>

    <div class="callback-inner section-container">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
            <!--i class="fa-solid fa-circle-nodes fa-3x" style="color: #c77dff;"></i-->

            <h2 class="text-3xl! pb-3 text-white!">Callback</h2>
            <hr />

            <p>
                If you have any further questions or suggestions, please feel
                free to message me on any of the social networks listed in the
                header. I am always available to answer your questions and would
                be happy to connect with new people.
                <br />
                You will be welcome.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .callback-bg {
        background: #151515 url("/media/IMG20220720225003.jpg") no-repeat center
            center;
        background-size: cover;
        height: auto;
        color: #ffffff;
    }

    .callback-overlay {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: #111111;
        opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .callback-inner {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        width: 30%;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .callback-inner {
            width: 80%;
        }
    }

    p {
        color: #b3aeba;
        text-align: justify;
        line-height: 1.2;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 400;
        padding-bottom: 1rem;
    }
</style>
